data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  Motivated Seller! Extended entry with 12-foot coffered ceilings. Formal dining room. Library with French-door entry. Family room with wall of windows opens to kitchen and morning area. Kitchen features island with built-in seating space. Spacious primary bedroom. Garden tub, separate glass-enclosed shower, double vanities and two walk-in closets in the primary bath. Two-car garage. Covered back patio.
